Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Schwarzschild Radius
Formula: r_s = 2GM/c²
Note:    Event horizon radius of a black hole

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Conservation of Mass
Formula: Reactants mass = Products mass
Note:    Mass is conserved in all chemical reactions

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Pythagorean Theorem
Formula: a² + b² = c²
Note:    Right triangle relationship; foundation of geometry

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Hubble's Law
Formula: v = H₀ × d
Note:    Universe is expanding; galaxies recede from us

Domain:  Biology
